## Frontend environment variables
##
## For local dev, point to your local backend.
## For AWS, point to your Elastic Beanstalk backend URL.

# Base URL for the backend server (no trailing slash).
# Examples:
#   http://localhost:5001
#   https://event-ticketing-backend-env.eba-8gmirmag.us-east-1.elasticbeanstalk.com
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5001
